author: Chris Danforth
title: Here’s What People Wore to COMME des GARÇONS’ FW17 Show in Paris
text:
Visit the original post to see all 25 images from this gallery. 
Always a highlight in the Paris Fashion Week schedule, COMME des GARÇONS recently unveiled its latest collection for FW17.
Posted outside the show, our street style lens captured the likes of A$AP Bari and 032c fashion editor Marc Goehring, as well as other fashion week regulars amongst the largely all-black affair. Our exclusive gallery includes looks from Vetements x Champion, as well as a few attendees faithfully rocking the vintage concert merch wave.
Now tune into what the fashion elite were rocking to Rick Owens and OFF-WHITE .
